full_text:
I listened to the podcast and I have to say those men were very unprofessional.  All they did was laugh, which showed to me, that they had no real way of disproving it either.  I am not sure why they chose to belittle the attempts we are making unless, for some reason, it is a threat to them.

They may not be impressed with us, but neither am I impressed with them.  If they were serious about finding out what this really is, they should have had Steve and Frank on the show so they could tell their thoughts on the subject.

Beth

